content:
[[module CSS]]
#page-content { position: relative; }
ul.modal-wrapper {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    height: 0;
    display: contents;
}
@keyframes fademodal {
  99% { visibility: hidden; }
  100% { visibility: visible; }
}
ul.modal-wrapper > li {
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.1rem;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 9;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease-out;
    animation: 0.15s fademodal;
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
}
ul.modal-wrapper > li.unfolded {
    visibility: visible;
    opacity: 1;
}
ul.modal-wrapper > li.folded {
    visibility: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
}

#page-content div#u-adult-warning {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: auto;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    color: black;
    text-shadow: none;
}
div#u-adult-warning > div#u-adult-header,
div#u-adult-warning > div#u-adult-header p { font-weight: bold; }
#page-content div#u-adult-warning a { color: #b01; }
#page-content div#u-adult-warning a.newpage { color: #d61; }
#page-content div#u-adult-warning a:not(.newpage):visited { color: #824; }

#u-adult-warning .content-descriptor {
    text-align: left;
    width: calc(100% - 3em);
    max-width: max-content;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-indent: -1.2em;
}
#u-adult-warning .content-descriptor br { display: none; }
#u-adult-warning .content-descriptor span {
    display: none;
    margin: 0.75em 0;
}
#u-adult-warning .content-descriptor span::before {
    content: "■";
    margin-right: 0.5em;
}
#u-adult-warning .choice {
    padding: 0.125em 0;
}
#u-adult-warning .footer-wikiwalk-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    grid-gap: 0.325em;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    background: unset;
    color: inherit;
}
#u-adult-warning .footer-wikiwalk-nav span[class^="ww-{$"] { display: none; }
[[/module]]


[[ul class="modal-wrapper"]]
[[li class="unfolded"]]
[[div id="adult-warning"]]
[[div id="adult-header"]]
成人内容
[[/div]]
本文章包含成人内容，可能并不适合所有读者阅读。
[[div_ class="content-descriptor"]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$gore} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]描绘血液、伤口或身体部位残缺的图像。[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$sexual-references} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]主要描写有性主题或语言，但并未描绘性爱场景。[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$sexually-explicit} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]明确描绘性爱场景。[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$sexual-assault} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]主要描写非自愿性爱场景。[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$child-abuse} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]描绘对儿童的严重虐待[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$self-harm} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]描绘自残[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$suicide} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]描绘自杀[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$torture} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]描绘酷刑[[/span]]
[[span style="display: [[#ifexpr {$custom} == 1 | block | none ]]"]]{$custom-content}[[/span]]
[[/div]]

若您的年龄已达 18 岁以上且希望阅读此类内容，则可点击继续以阅览上述内容。
[[div_ class="foldable-list-container choice"]]
[# 继续]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="choice"]]
[/ 回到首页]
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="footer-wikiwalk-nav"]]
[[span class="ww-{$prev}"]]<< [[[{$prev}|]]] |[[/span]][[span class="ww-{$current}"]]{$current}[[/span]][[span class="ww-{$next}"]]| [[[{$next}|]]] >>[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[/div]]
[[/li]]
[[/ul]]


[[iftags +组件]]
[[div style="border: solid 2px #ededed; padding: 0.5rem; margin: 4px;"]]
这是一个工作人员用以标记成人内容的组件。
若需使用，请将以下代码放置在页面顶部：

[[div class="blockquote"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki-cn:component:adult-content-warning@@
|gore=1
|sexual-references=1
|sexually-explicit=1
|sexual-assault=1
|child-abuse=1
|self-harm=1
|suicide=1
|torture=1
|custom=1 |custom-content=“定制内容”警告

|prev=前一页面编号
|current=当前页面标题
|next=下一页面编号
]]
[[/div]]

请忽略不使用的警告。只需使用经批准的自定义内容警告。在没有输入内容指定时，Wikiwalk 将不会出现。更多信息请参考[[[adult-content-warning-guide|成人内容警告指导]]]或联系[http://05command.wikidot.com/maintenance-and-ancillary-staff-team-main 成人内容管理小组][[footnote]]**译注：**此团队在中分不存在，仅适用于英站。[[/footnote]]成员。

若需在使用 listpages 显示一系列段落页面的文章中使用，请将该组件放置在第一个段落页内。

[[/div]]
[[/iftags]]
